{
  "stem": "6777.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And during the war it got smaller and part off it was turned into a resort, Jewish resort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Otwock is-- I wouldn't say a suburb-- it was a line, a railway line from Warsaw towards the northeast.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a line which was to later used for going to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think so, it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, Vera and all the kids, Vera and Nina, Roman and Eva, they went to the sanatorium, it was called, in Otwock.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was also a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was not part of the Polish ghetto, but it was the Otwock ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could, you could go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went by car.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, they went to Otwock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Ida, the grandmother, she was smuggled out of the ghetto with some furniture on a wagon, horse-drawn wagon with some furniture, which was supposed to go for the Germans in a building.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We put her and she was said to be the cleaning lady for when the furniture arrived in the new building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'd been waiting already for this wagon in a side street of Warsaw with another horse-drawn wagon and have transferred her from the Jewish one to the Polish one.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And taken Ida, together with the furniture, into our new flat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when Otwock was nearly finished, we got the new that it would be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we took them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I provided for them a little house two stations away from Otwock in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the children with Ida stayed there, and Vera, with Nina, went back to the ghetto, to her husband.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I told you, they've been-- we've been divided.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ida and the twins they're in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vera and Nina went back to the ghetto to her husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I've been floating everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
